  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you're right, there was-- of course, he gave up one very lucrative practice in order to go into the unknown, really, into a new field, new for him, relatively new for the-- for the audience, for the-- for the public.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was-- it was a very risky thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he was convinced that this was the thing to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and-- there was-- he really felt that he had no choice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- that-- that's an interesting, interesting situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Psychoanalysts are not [SIGHS] sought or gone to by poor people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Therefore, to have the kind of patients that can pay for your services, you have to keep up the kind of-- the kind of front that, that, that they expect.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we moved into a-- into the most elegant part of Berlin, a huge apartment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was, in fact-- it had been the apartment of Franz Grunbaum.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was getting a divorce at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he moved into a-- first, he stayed in a, in a few rooms in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he, he moved into, into a flat, another apartment nearby, a smaller apartment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and-- however, we didn't have-- we had nice furniture that we brought from Konigsberg.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it wasn't anything like as elegant as the-- as you would expect coming in from the-- from the-- from the street into this-- [? this ?] house and-- or the area.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were not living in the way we were clothed, the way we ate, the way we-- generally, we had-- we were not living like rich people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we lived, we, we, we resided, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in an expensive place, which must have cost him dearly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- but, but he had to establish himself.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
